import React from 'react'
import { Image, Segment, Grid, Header, Form, Button, Responsive } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import * as contact from '../Assets/contact.png';

class ContactUs extends React.Component {

 render() {

   return (
     <React.Fragment>
      <Responsive minWidth={Responsive.onlyTablet.minWidth}>
        <Grid textAlign='center' style={{ height: '100vh'}} verticalAlign='middle'>

            <Grid.Row>
              <Image src={contact} style = {{paddingLeft:'1em', marginTop:'-2%'}}/>
            </Grid.Row>
            <Grid.Row>
            <Segment raised style = {{padding: '5%'}}>
            <Form>
              <Form.Group widths='equal'>
                <Form.Field>
                  <label style={{textAlign:'left'}}>* First Name</label>
                  <input style = {{borderRadius:'100px'}} placeholder='First Name' />
                </Form.Field>
                <Form.Field>
                  <label style={{textAlign:'left'}}>* Last Name</label>
                  <input style = {{borderRadius:'100px'}} placeholder='Last Name' />
                </Form.Field>
              </Form.Group>
              <Form.Field>
                <label style={{textAlign:'left'}}>* Email </label>
                <input style = {{borderRadius:'100px'}} placeholder='Email' />
              </Form.Field>
              <Form style={{textAlign:'left', marginBottom:'3%'}}>
                <Form.TextArea style = {{borderRadius:'10px'}} label ='* Message' placeholder='Message' />
              </Form>
              <Button fluid circular type='submit' style = {{backgroundColor:'#EDAC86', color:'white'}}>Send</Button>
            </Form>
            </Segment>
          </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>

      </Responsive>
      <Responsive {...Responsive.onlyMobile}>
      </Responsive>
    </React.Fragment>
  );
 }
}
export default ContactUs;
